A Bronze key is an item that is created by using gypsum and a vial of liquid on a tin, using it on the chained key, adding Cupric ore powder and Tin ore powder, adding it to a tin and heating it over a Bunsen burner during the Miss Cheevers challenge as part of the Recruitment Drive quest. It can be used to open the door to end the challenge.
